  "title": "Assistand Branch manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position Available: Assistant Branch Manager</strong><br />📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East / Tampines - (APRIL)<br />🏢 <strong>Company:</strong> Maidbook Employment Agency</p><p>We are looking for a <strong>self-motivated and responsible Assistant Branch Manager</strong> to support and manage our Jurong East branch.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in managing daily branch operations</p></li><li><p>Be <strong>in charge of the branch</strong> when required</p></li><li><p>Supervise staff and ensure smooth workflow</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries and service standards</p></li><li><p>Support sales, follow-ups, and branch performance</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with MOM and company policies</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Self-motivated, responsible, and proactive</p></li><li><p>Good communication and leadership skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently</p></li><li><p>Experience in employment agency or customer service is an advantage</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Interested candidates, please contact us or send your resume.</strong></p>",
